Charlotte Roach was involved in a car accident in 2010 . 
  She was left with punctured lungs and broken bones . 
  Triathlete and business partner Rosemary Pringle gave up ordinary clothes for 40 days to raise money for London's Air Ambulance Service . 
  Charlotte and Rosemary dressed up in different costumes for every day of lent . 
  The charity saved her life after she was injured in a crash in November 2010 . 
 